&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop automated build, test, and release infrastructures.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Set and uphold the standard for engineering processes to support high-quality engineering, including style and code checking, test harnesses, and release packaging.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
