&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(29, 28, 29) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(29, 28, 29); font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience with API development and integration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
